ness%20Insider%20that%20he%20would%20not%20encourage%20people%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-booming-is-phd-necessary-machine-learning-jobs-workers-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20a%20Ph.D.%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20AI%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20itself%20is%20going%20to%20be%20gone%20by%20the%20time%20you%20finish%20a%20Ph.D.%20Even%20things%20like%20applying%20AI%20to%20robotics%20will%20be%20solved%20by%20then.%20So%20either%20get%20into%20something%20niche%20like%20AI%20for%20biology%2C%20which%20is%20still%20in%20its%20very%20early%20stages%2C%20or%20just%20don't%20get%20into%20anything%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Tarifi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarifi%2C%2042%2C%20got%20his%20Ph.D.%20in%20AI%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Florida%20in%202012.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejoined%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202012%20and%20spent%20nearly%20a%20decade%20with%20the%20search%20giant.%20In%202021%2C%20Tarifi%20started%20his%20own%20AI%20startup%2C%20Integral%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarifi%20said%20doctoral%20studies%20are%20an%20ordeal%20that%20only%20%26quot%3Bweird%20people%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20much%20like%20he%20was%20%E2%80%94%20should%20undertake%2C%20because%20it%20involves%20sacrificing%20%26quot%3Bfive%20years%20of%20your%20life%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20pain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20anyone%20should%20ever%20do%20a%20Ph.D.%20unless%20they%20are%20obsessed%20with%20the%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20Tarifi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20with%20the%20world%20advancing%20as%20fast%20as%20it%20is%2C%20you%20can%20achieve%20a%20lot%20more%20outside%20school%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20unsure%2C%20you%20should%20definitely%20default%20to%20'no%2C'%20and%20focus%20on%20just%20living%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Tarifi%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20wil