easily%20written%20an%20MBA-style%20case%20study%20on%20why%20Figma%20wouldn't%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20market%20seemed%20too%20small%2C%20the%20competition%20too%20intense%2C%20and%20the%20margins%20unworkable%2C%20Rohan%20said.%20There%20were%20many%20reasons%20to%20doubt%20its%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERohan%2C%20however%2C%20said%20he%20saw%20potential%20in%20its%20founders%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-empowering-generalist-behaviour-figma-ceo-tech-design-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDylan%20Field%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Evan%20Wallace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDylan%20and%20Evan%20were%20just%20exceptional%2C%20and%20they%20had%20a%20vision%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20cofounders%20whom%20he%20first%20met%20during%20their%20seed%20pitch%20in%202013%20when%20he%20was%20an%20investor%20at%20Index%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndex%20led%20Figma's%20%243.87%20million%20seed%20round%20and%20continued%20backing%20the%20company%20through%20multiple%20funding%20rounds%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%20Rohan%20served%20as%20Figma's%20first%20board%20director%20from%202013%20to%202015.%20He's%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20board%2C%20but%20remains%20on%20the%20company's%20cap%20table.%20He%20attended%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ipo-party-wall-street-photos-2025-7%23revelers-lined-up-at-two-free-merch-booths-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIPO%20celebration%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20and%20still%20keeps%20in%20touch%20with%20Field%2C%20who%20is%20now%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFigma%20is%20a%20digital%20design%20tool%20that%20allows%20people%20to%20create%20and%20collaborate%20on%20creative%20projects%2C%20including%20websites%2C%20apps%2C%20and%20logos.%20When%20it%20launched%20its%20first%20tool%20in%202015%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20real-time%2C%20collaborative%20online%20design%20was%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3Bheresy%2C%26quot%3B%20Field%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Figma's%20website%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20generational%20assault%20on%20top-down%2C%20siloed%20models%20of%20decision-making%20and%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20identity%20of%20many%20designers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Some%20in%20the%20field%20even%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20was%20the%20future%20of%20design%2C%20they%20were%20changing%20careers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20it%20had%20built%20a%20base%20of%20more%20than%204%20million%20users.%20That's%20when%20it%20attracted%20the%20attention%20of%20Adobe%2C%20which%20announced%20plans%20to%20acquire%20the%20company.%20But%20after%20regulatory%20pressure%2C%20the%20%2420%20billion%20deal%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ipo-investors-better-outcome-adobe-deal-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFigma%20finally%20went%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%2C%20the%20offering%20was%20more%20than%2040%20times%20oversubscribed%2C%20and%20the%20stock%20more%20than%20tripled%20its%20IPO%20price%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20Rohan%20said%20it%20was%20Field%20and%20Wallace's%20authenticity%20and%20their%20sense%20of%20self%20that%20first%20won%20him%20over.%20These%20have%20become%20some%20of%20the%20top%20traits%20he%20looks%20for%20in%20founders%20when%20he's%20considering%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20always%2C%20like%2C%20a%20long%20kind%20of%20story%20to%20what%20they're%20building%2C%20or%20the%20skill%20sets%20that%20they're%20using%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20just%20fits%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnother%20element%20that%20is%20within%20that%20concept%20of%20authenticity%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20self-awareness.%26quot%3B%20Those%20are%20founders%20who%20know%20%26quot%3Bwho%20they%20are%2C%20and%20they%20know%20what%20they're%20good%20at%2C%20and%20they%20know%20what%20they%20need%20to%20build.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20several%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ipo-donation-440-million-marin-community-foundation-evan-wallace-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFigma%20has%20released%20a%20slate%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20new%20features%2C%20including%20tools%20for%20ideation%2C%20prototyping%2C%20and%20website%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERohan%20said%20that%20watching%20Figma%20grow%20has%20also%20given%20him%20%26quot%3Bmore%20confidence%20in%20the%20way%20that%20I%20underwrite%20seed%20investing.%26quot%3B%20He's%20now%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Otherwise%20Fund%2C%20where%20some%20of%20his%20top%20investments%20include%20Hugging%20Face%2C%20Notion%2C%20Robinhood%2C%20and%20Vanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-founders-dylan-field-evan-wallace-early-investor-terrance-rohan-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755456455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a223a7194a2d49b8aeb39c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-founders-dylan-field-evan-wallace-early-investor-terrance-rohan-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Terrence%20Rohan%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Otherwise%20Fund%2C%20was%20one%20of%20Figma's%20first%20backers.%20He%20spoke%20to%20BI%20about%20the%20traits%20he%20looks%20for%20in%20a%20founder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-founders-dylan-field-evan-wallace-early-investor-terrance-rohan-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Armaan%E2%80%99s%20first%20wife%20Payal%20pregnant%2C%20not%20second%20wife%20Kritika%22%2C%22content%