ses%20to%20incorporate%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20we%20also%20want%20their%20physical%20assets%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20County%20Commissioner%20Michael%20Naft%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Clark%20County%20is%20home%20to%20Las%20Vegas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELen%20Jessup%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20with%20Desert%20Forge%20Ventures%2C%20which%20is%20based%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20and%20invests%20in%20early-stage%20companies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he's%20seen%20more%20corporations%20choose%20Nevada%20as%20a%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20founders%20moving%20here%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20from%20California%20because%20it's%20adjacent%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they're%20coming%20from%20all%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Jessup%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20being%20drawn%20to%20Nevada%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20including%20no%20state%20income%20tax%20on%20individuals%2C%20no%20capital%20gains%20tax%2C%20and%20what%20Jessup%20described%20as%20lighter%20regulations.%20While%20Nevada%20doesn't%20have%20an%20individual%20income%20tax%2C%20it%20does%20enforce%20a%20commerce%20tax%20on%20businesses%20earning%20more%20than%20%244%20million%20in%20gross%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%20Mignano%2C%20a%20founding%20partner%20of%20SSM%20Law%20PC%20who%20represents%20emerging%20tech%20companies%2C%20said%20the%20different%20tax%20structures%20%26quot%3Bmay%20make%20less%20of%20a%20difference%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20early%20stage%20because%20%26quot%3Brevenue%20is%20not%20yet%20high%2C%20but%20at%20the%20later%20stages%20of%20a%20company's%20lifecycle%2C%20this%20can%20absolutely%20add%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225230%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Welcome%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a0dbac194a2d49b8aeb251%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20businesses%20are%20considering%20making%20Nevada%20their%20home.%3Cp%3EDeFodi%20Images%2FDeFodi%20Images%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20County%20is%20hoping%20to%20draw%20more%20companies%20to%20the%20region%20by%20developing%20what%20it's%20calling%20an%20%26quot%3Binnovation%20district.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20something%20that%20we've%20been%20really%20methodical%20about.%20We've%20gotten%20stakeholders%20together%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20Clark%20County's%20innovation%20district%20is%20really%20about%20lifting%20up%20what's%20happening%20here%20organically%20and%20using%20those%20assets%20to%20attract%20more%20like-minded%20businesses%20and%20individuals%20to%20be%20part%20of%20that%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Naft%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Switch%20facility%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Nevada%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68991ba8a17a8c5b40529e2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Switch%20facility%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Nevada.%3Cp%3ELiv%20Paggiarino%2FLas%20Vegas%20Review-Journal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Jessup%2C%20getting%20companies%20to%20incorporate%20in%20Nevada%20is%20a%20way%20to%20expand%20the%20state's%20economy%2C%20which%20mostly%20relies%20on%20its%20hospitality%20and%20tourism%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20goal%20is%2C%2010%20years%20down%20the%20road%2C%20I%20want%20to%20have%20helped%20to%20create%20companies%20in%20tech%20and%20biotech%20%E2%80%94%20so%2C%20outside%20of%20gaming%2C%20hospitality%2C%20sports%2C%20and%20entertainment%20%E2%80%94%20that%20add%20to%20the%20ecosystem%20and%20help%20to%20diversify%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Jessup%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Las%20Vegas%20Convention%20and%20Visitors%20Authority%20reported%20that%20the%20number%20of%20visitors%20declined%2011.3%25%20this%20June%20compared%20to%20the%20same%