0cost%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20plant.%20But%20I%20wanted%20to%20have%20them%20in%20my%20collection.%20I%20started%20using%20the%20profits%20of%20the%20sales%20to%20invest%20in%20more%20varieties%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20her%20collection%20has%20grown%20to%20an%20impressive%20300%20varieties%20sourced%20from%20across%20India%20and%20places%20as%20far%20off%20as%20Thailand%20and%20Brazil.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20such%20a%20lovely%20view%20when%20all%20the%20varieties%20bloom%20in%20different%20colours%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20passion%20and%20profession%20efficiently%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvathy%20looked%20after%20her%20garden%20every%20day%20until%20last%20year%20when%20she%20secured%20a%20job%20at%20an%20IT%20company%20in%20Kochi%20after%20completion%20of%20her%20studies.%20Despite%20challenges%20such%20as%20managing%20her%20full-time%20job%20and%20adjusting%20to%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20needs%20based%20on%20seasonal%20variations%2C%20she%20thrives%20in%20her%20dual%20role.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20weekend%2C%20she%20manages%20to%20come%20back%20to%20her%20hometown%20to%20manage%20her%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20also%20hired%20two%20women%20workers%20who%20take%20care%20of%20the%20garden%20when%20I%20am%20not%20around.%20I%20have%20taught%20them%20all%20the%20expertise%20required%20to%20do%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fportulaca-3-1722572904.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20her%20business%20grows%2C%20Parvathy%20dreams%20of%20balancing%20her%20work%20and%20passion%20while%20expanding%20her%20venture.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fportulaca-3-1722572904.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fportulaca-3-1722572904-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fportulaca-3-1722572904-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fportulaca-3-1722572904-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fportulaca-3-1722572904-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359458%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20Parvathy%E2%80%99s%20collection%20has%20grown%20to%20an%20impressive%20300%20varieties.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20mastered%20the%20nuances%20of%20portulaca%20care%20by%20focusing%20on%20essentials%20like%20direct%20sunlight%2C%20minimal%20watering%2C%20regular%20pruning%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20organic%20fertilisers%20like%20cow%20dung.%20Besides%2C%20portulacas%20are%20known%20for%20their%20vibrant%20blooms%20and%20minimal%20care%20requirements.%20This%20fits%20perfectly%20into%20her%20busy%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20challenges%20in%20portulaca%20farming%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20rainy%20season%2C%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20a%20few%20varieties%20like%20Jumbo.%20I%20repot%20these%20plants%20and%20maintain%20new%20cuttings%20so%20that%20their%20roots%20do%20not%20rot%20in%20the%20excess%20rain%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20portulaca%20farming%2C%20she%20manages%20to%20get%2050-100%20orders%20in%20a%20day.%20With%20this%2C%20she%20says%20to%20generate%20an%20additional%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20As%20her%20business%20grows%2C%20Parvathy%20dreams%20of%20balancing%20her%20work%20and%20passion%20while%20expanding%20her%20venture.%20She%20also%20encourages%20others%20to%20opt%20for%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20in%20need%20of%20additional%20income%20can%20do%20this%20as%20a%20business%20also.%20The%20key%20is%20to%20grow%20low-maintenance%20but%20high%20demand%20plants%20like%20portulaca%20and%20find%20a%20trustworthy%20team%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20work%20in%20your%20absence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajani%20Mohanan%2C%20who%20has%20seen%20Parvathy%20toil%20hard%20while%20managing%20both%20the%20office%20and%20the%20farm%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20started%20this%20business%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20when%20she%20was%20just%20a%20college%20student.%20This%20has%20become%20an%20extra%20source%20of%20income%20for%20her%20and%20she%20is%20able%20to%20manage%20all%20her%20expenses%20with%20ease%20and%20have%20some%20left%20for%20enjoyment%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Parvathy%20returns%20to%20Kochi%20for%20her%20work%2C%20Rajani%20takes%20over%20some%20of%20her%20responsibilities%20here%20like%20helping%20with%20order%20packaging.%20She%20shares%20how%20the%20business%20has%20also%20helped%20them%20bond%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvathy%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20not%20just%20one%20of%20entrepreneurial%20success%20but%20also%20a%20lesson%20in%20pursuing%20one%E2%80%99s%20passion%20against%20the%20odds.%20Her%20journey%20from%20a%20hobbyist%20to%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20highlights%20the%20potential%20of%20turning%20a%20simple%20passion%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348172%2Fflower-farmer-in-karnataka-bengaluru-srikanth-bollapally-grows-roses-gerbera-carnations-making-crores-annually%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20her%20story%20continues%20to%20unfold%2C%20one%20bloom%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20compliments%20and%20appreciation%20that%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20I%20am%20doing%20very%20well.%20But%20if%20I