Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Sun%20Belt's%20housing%20market%20is%20cooling%20as%20Northern%20markets%20heat%20up%2C%20according%20to%20Bankrate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECost%20of%20living%20increases%2C%20like%20home%20insurance%2C%20in%20Southern%20states%20make%20them%20less%20affordable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20cities%20in%20Florida%20that%20were%20the%20hottest%20markets%20two%20years%20ago%20are%20now%20some%20of%20the%20coldest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Southern%20housing%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-are-people-moving-florida-home-prices-cost-of-living-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eespecially%20Florida's%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20boomed%20as%20record%20numbers%20of%20people%20moved%20to%20the%20region%20for%20its%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20relatively%20affordable%20homes.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankrate.com%2Freal-estate%2Fhousing-heat-index%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBankrate's%202025%20Housing%20Heat%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20the%20trend%20is%20now%20reversing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Ostrowski%2C%20Bankrate's%20housing%20market%20analyst%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomer-homeowners-retirees-moved-from-sunbelt-to-midwest-2025-4%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHome%2520prices%2520and%2520rents%2520have%2Careas%252C%2520has%2520stayed%2520relatively%2520affordable.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Sun%20Belt%20has%20lost%20its%20edge%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eas%20buyer%20demand%20fades%20and%20home%20sellers%20slash%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Northeasterners%20were%20fleeing%20for%20the%20Sun%20Belt%2C%20but%20that%20trend%20has%20slowed%20and%20even%20reversed%2C%26quot%3B%20Ostrowski%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20in%20the%20North%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20just%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20inventory%2C%20and%20with%20limited%20choices%2C%20buyers%20are%20bidding%20up%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%20at%20Bankrate%20analyzed%20212%20metros%20in%20the%20US%2C%20considering%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20year-over-year%20appreciation%20of%20home%20values%20%E2%80%94%20the%20most%20heavily%20weighted%20factor%20at%2040%25%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20employment%20levels%2C%20job%20growth%2C%20population%20trends%2C%20homes%20listed%20for%20sale%2C%20and%20typical%20selling%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bankrate's%20index%2C%20the%20Northeast%20had%20a%20strong%20showing%20at%20the%20top%2C%20with%20three%20of%20the%20top%20five%20hottest%20markets.%20This%20is%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%202023%20rankings%2C%20in%20which%20the%20hottest%20markets%20were%20largely%20Southern%20cities.%20The%20New%20Haven-Milford%20metropolitan%20area%20of%20Connecticut%2C%20for%20example%2C%20found%20its%20way%20to%20the%20top%20five%20in%20this%20year's%20ranking%20but%20was%20ranked%2082nd%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%20Florida%20dominated%20the%20coolest%20markets%2C%20taking%20four%20of%20the%20bottom%20five%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20prices%20are%20increasing%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%20but%20in%20Florida%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-home-insurance-prices-premium-effect-from-hurricanes-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-eliminate-property-taxes-every-state-tax-rate-map-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproperty%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20increasing%20as%20well%2C%20homeowners%20are%20feeling%20even%20more%20crunched%20%E2%80%94%20and%20prospective%20homebuyers%20would%20rather%20wait%20it%20out%20instead%20of%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bankrate's%20ranking%2C%20the%20North%20Port-Sarasota-Bradenton%20metro%20in%20Florida%20was%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20in%20the%20country%20in%202023%2C%20landing%20in%20the%20top%20five.%20However%2C%20this%20year%2C%20it's%20in%20the%20bottom%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20visited%20a%20number%20of%20open%20houses%20in%20that%20market%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20a%20lot%20of%20lonely%20listing%20agents%20sitting%20in%20kitchens%20and%20waiting%20for%20buyers%20to%20come%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20Ostrowski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20five%20hottest%20and%20five%20coldest%20markets%20in%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20Bankrate.%20Median%20home-sale%20prices%20are%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FZillow.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZillow.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20population%20estimates%20come%20from%20the%20US%20Census%20Bureau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20hottest%20markets%20in%20the%20US%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Historic%20district%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6789503310c98eace912b6e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHistoric%20district%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina.%3Cp%3ESean%20Pavone%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E5.%20York-Hanover%2C%20Pennsylvania%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224234%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22York%2C%20Pennsylvania%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d76a9d62e22af2c0b2a40d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222508%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPopulation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20471%2C240%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnemployment%20overall%20rank%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2079%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne-year%20appreciation%20rank%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2017%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EActive%20listings%20ov