best-vegetarian-dishes-from-around-the-world-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epopular%20Nepali%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E%20similar%20to%20a%20Chinese%20dumpling.%20I%20hate%20cooking%2C%20absolutely%20despise%20it.%20So%2C%20I%20wasn't%20looking%20forward%20to%20this%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20my%20fellow%20travelers%20and%20I%20started%20opening%20up%20about%20our%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20who%20we%20were%2C%20why%20we%20decided%20on%20this%20trip%20to%20Nepal%20%E2%80%94%20the%20momo%20making%20was%20just%20something%20to%20keep%20our%20hands%20busy%20while%20we%20did%20the%20important%20work%20of%20getting%20to%20know%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20poor%20momo%20chef%20kept%20trying%20to%20interrupt%20our%20conversation%20to%20tell%20us%20the%20history%20of%20momos%20and%20how%20to%20perfect%20our%20momo-making%20skills%2C%20but%20the%20group%20had%20instantly%20bonded.%20Conversation%20took%20off%20immediately%2C%20and%20we%20were%20on%20our%20way%20to%20becoming%20instant%20travel%20besties%20on%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20left%20our%20momo-making%20session%2C%20it%20was%20pouring%20rain%20outside%2C%20but%20we%20just%20laughed%20as%20we%20jumped%20through%20puddles%20and%20made%20our%20way%20back%20to%20the%20hotel.%20The%20tone%20of%20the%20trip%20was%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223df32a78-f60e-48e0-aee6-c139c8c09966%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20had%20countless%20adventures%20together%20and%20a%20minor%20hiccup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20on%20metal%20bridge%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Nepal%20forest%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689ccd20cfc04e97619b5aa0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKoutsky%20walking%20across%20one%20of%20the%20many%20suspension%20bridges%20that%20can%20be%20found%20throughout%20Nepal.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Judy%20Koutsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspiritual-healing-trip-to-kathmandu-nepal-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estarted%20in%20Kathmandu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20every%20two%20nights%20we%20moved%20to%20a%20new%20city.%20That%20meant%20we%20had%20plenty%20of%20places%20to%20explore%2C%20plus%20plenty%20of%20van%20time%20for%20talking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhaktapur%2C%20we%20explored%20Durbar%20and%20Dattatreya%20Square.%20We%20hiked%20through%20the%20forest%20up%20to%20the%20top%20of%20Champa%20Devi%2C%20where%20we%20took%20in%20views%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20mountains%20and%20learned%20that%20Nepal%20is%20home%20to%20eight%20of%20the%2010%20tallest%20mountains%20in%20the%20world%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmount-everest-10th-deadliest-mountain-himalayas-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMount%20Everest%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Pharping%2C%20we%20visited%20religious%20landmarks%20at%20the%20Buddhist%20Asura%20Cave%2C%20Vajrayogini%20Temple%2C%20and%20Sheshnarayan%20Hindu%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20then%20drove%20on%20to%20Royal%20Chitwan%20National%20Park%2C%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20spots%20and%20favorite%20days%20of%20the%20trip.%20Our%20plan%20was%20to%20bike%20through%20a%20village%20and%20end%20up%20on%20the%20water%20for%20sunset%2C%20enjoying%20drinks%20and%20appetizers.%20It%20was%20notably%20hot%20that%20day%2C%20and%20one%20of%20my%20new%20travel%20besties%20told%20me%20later%20that%20she%20saw%20me%20sweating%20profusely%20and%20smiling%20manically%20while%20I%20kept%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20this%20so%20much.%26quot%3B%20And%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20trip%2C%20there%20were%20hiccups%20along%20the%20way%20%E2%80%94%20we%20all%20took%20turns%20having%20traveler's%20diarrhea%20(we%20pooled%20our%20Imodium%20and%20rehydration%20tablets)%20%E2%80%94%20but%20even%20the%20hiccups%20brought%20us%20together.%20We%20took%20turns