he%20different%20households%3B%20which%20ones%20are%20run%20by%20single%20women%2C%20which%20ones%20are%20run%20by%20widows%2C%20which%20ones%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F482390%2Fkerala-couple-quit-it-jobs-turns-family-land-into-organic-farm-trains-15000-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edepend%20on%20farming%20for%20their%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20which%20homes%20have%20people%20with%20a%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20data%20is%20fed%20into%20the%20app%2C%20basis%20which%20it%20assesses%20which%20families%20will%20most%20benefit%20from%20the%20programme.%20The%20assessment%20metrics%20are%20vulnerability%2C%20asset%20holdings%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20working%20in%20the%20family%2C%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20of%20the%20app%20is%20that%20it%20removes%20any%20inconsistencies%20in%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20Vinod%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20if%20a%20person%20visits%20a%20family%20of%20daily%20wage%20workers%20during%20the%20harvest%20season%20when%20they%20are%20getting%20a%20stable%20income%2C%20they%20might%20have%20a%20completely%20different%20idea%20about%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20income%20status%20compared%20to%20if%20they%20would%20have%20visited%20the%20family%20in%20the%20monsoon%20season%2C%20when%20the%20sowing%20is%20done%20and%20there%20is%20no%20work.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20where%20the%20app%20comes%20in%2C%20removing%20inconsistencies%20in%20human%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20app%20works%20is%20that%20it%20calculates%20the%20average%20pay%20that%20the%20person%20is%20getting%20in%20a%20year%2C%20by%20factoring%20in%20what%20kind%20of%20work%20the%20person%20does.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20app%20also%20flags%20any%20inconsistencies%20here%3B%20for%20instance%2C%20if%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359592%2Flinkedin-for-blue-collar-daily-wager-labourer-digital-labour-chowk-job-search-migrant-workers-bihar-uttar-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperson%20is%20doing%20daily%20labour%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mentions%20that%20they%20earn%20a%20very%20high%20amount%2C%20the%20app%20would%20flag%20it%20immediately%2C%20as%20it%20has%20already%20been%20programmed%20with%20information%20on%20the%20pay%20for%20different%20types%20of%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinod%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20every%20family%20is%20asked%20two%20questions%3A%20what%20kind%20of%20work%20they%20do%20and%20what%20the%20pay%20is%20per%20day.%20The%20data%20is%20then%20fed%20into%20the%20app%2C%20and%20it%20goes%20ahead%20and%20produces%20a%20holistic%20picture%20of%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20economic%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20that%20selection%20is%20done%20at%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20family%2C%20Vinod%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20family%20is%20claiming%20to%20have%20five%20goats%2C%20we%20ask%20to%20see%20the%20goats.%20We%20also%20require%20a%20selfie%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20front%20of%20the%20house%2C%20and%20the%20location%20to%20be%20recorded%20for%20future%20visits.%20Then%20follows%20a%20two-step%20OTP%20process%20and%20submission%20of%20the%20selection%20form.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fleap-300-eradicating-poverty-1-1755092242.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20selection%20process%20is%20done%20at%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20family%20to%20check%20if%20they%20are%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20the%20programme%20and%20will%20benefit%20from%20it%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fleap-300-eradicating-poverty-1-1755092242.jpg%201