%2FSubrat-Nath-1-1715319467-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349609%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Subrat%20maintains%20a%20garden%20of%20400%20plants%20like%20100%20varieties%20of%20water%20lilies%20and%20lotuses.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMiyazaki%20mango%2C%201%2C000%20petal%20lotus%2C%20and%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Subrat%E2%80%99s%20interest%20piqued%20in%20growing%20rare%20flowering%20and%20fruiting%20plants%20at%20home.%20With%20a%20simple%20google%20search%2C%20he%20read%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246852%2Frare-exotic-plants-saplings-propagation-urban-gardener-organic-vertical-hanging-garden-bhopal-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erare%20plants%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20warm%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20keeping%20rare%20plants%20inside%20my%20garden.%20Sometimes%20it%20is%20challenging%20as%20well%2C%20given%20the%20temperature%20here%20rises%20to%2046%20degrees%20in%20the%20summer.%20But%20this%20challenge%20is%20what%20exactly%20makes%20it%20fun%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20control%20the%20temperature%2C%20he%20has%20established%20a%20small%20greenhouse%20where%20he%20keeps%20new%20saplings%20for%202-3%20months%20to%20help%20them%20acclimatise.%20%E2%80%9CI%20introduce%20them%20to%20direct%20sunlight%20slowly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20Miyazaki%20mango%20plant%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20planted%20it%20directly%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20my%20house.%20Its%20sapling%20cost%20me%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20take%20any%20risk.%20I%20let%20the%20sapling%20settle%20into%20the%20soil.%20After%20two%20months%2C%20I%20added%20cow%20dung%2